            <title><![CDATA[Nintendo posts cute and mysterious animated short film, but is it teasing Pikmin?]]></title>
            <link>https://www.eurogamer.net/nintendo-posts-cute-and-mysterious-animated-short-film-but-is-it-teasing-pikmin</link>
