            <title><![CDATA[One of Borderlands' most hated characters seems to have been cut from Borderlands 4]]></title>
            <link>https://www.eurogamer.net/one-of-borderlands-most-hated-characters-seems-to-have-been-cut-from-borderlands-4</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/one-of-borderlands-most-hated-characters-seems-to-have-been-cut-from-borderlands-4.1318531/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>
      <article data-ads="true" data-article-type="news" data-article-group="news" data-paywalled="false" data-premium="false" data-sponsored="false" data-type="article">


<header data-component="article-header">
  

    <div id="main-content">
        

        <p>Ava few files for your troubles.</p>

    </div>


  <p>


  <figure>
      <picture data-src-full="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/borderlands-4-finger-guns-steam-store-art.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1920&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=70&amp;format=jpg&amp;auto=webp" src="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/borderlands-4-finger-guns-steam-store-art.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1920&amp;fit=bounds&amp;quality=70&amp;format=jpg&amp;auto=webp">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/borderlands-4-finger-guns-steam-store-art.jpg?width=380&amp;quality=70&amp;format=jpg&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 1dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/borderlands-4-finger-guns-steam-store-art.jpg?width=380&amp;quality=70&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=1.5&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 1.5dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/borderlands-4-finger-guns-steam-store-art.jpg?width=380&amp;quality=70&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=1.75&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 1.75dppx)">
        <source srcset="https://assetsio.gnwcdn.com/borderlands-4-finger-guns-steam-store-art.jpg?width=380&amp;quality=70&amp;format=jpg&amp;dpr=2&amp;auto=webp" media="(max-width: 549px) and (max-resolution: 2dppx)">
